translations: n．十英镑纸币（复数）：英国货币单位，指面值为10英镑的纸币。
· I have three tenners in my wallet.
我钱包里有三张十英镑的纸币。

sentences.sentence: Some historians trace it back to the summer of 2003, when Roman Abramovich pitched up in London and began shovelling tenners on to the glowing embers in the furnace at Stamford Bridge.
sentences.translation: 有些历史学家认为这种感情的起点应该是2003年的夏天，彼时罗曼·阿布拉莫维奇君临伦敦，开始为斯坦福桥的崛起贡献着自己无穷无尽的英镑。
